## Import.Importers.PathImporter.import() method

Imports an item, extracting any resources or candidates from it and returns an optional list of additional importable items derived from it.

**Signature:**

```typescript
import(item: IImportable, __manager: ResourceManager): DetailedResult<IImportable[], ImporterResultDetail>;
```
